{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Katana Dragon</strong> is an <strong>action-RPG adventure and dungeons exploration</strong>, where you play as the ninjas Shin and Nobi in their quest to end the curse that hangs over Sogen.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Learn ninja skills, upgrade your Dragon Gems, equip the Cursed Seals and level up. Avoid traps, solve puzzles and fight powerful enemies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Your ninja way begins!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>EXPLORE A VAST WORLD</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303010/extras/scroll01_low.gif?t=1735350370\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>The beautiful lands of Sogen</strong> are waiting to be discovered. The whole map, their secrets, the challenges and even the dungeons have been <strong>hand designed</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>MASTER NINJA SKILLS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303010/extras/scroll02_low.gif?t=1735350370\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Learn new ninja skills</strong> that will help you solve puzzles, defeat enemies and even reach new areas and discover their secrets.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>FIGHT AGAINST ENEMIES</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303010/extras/scroll03_low.gif?t=1735350370\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Fight against Gokais</strong>, powerful creatures capable of breathing fire, biting or even flying. Will you be able to register them all in your <i>Gokairium</i>?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>DIVE INTO DUNGEONS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303010/extras/scroll04_low.gif?t=1735350370\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Explore dungeons, wells and caves</strong> to find treasures and test your training. Walk through rooms, avoid their traps, and fight against <strong>bosses </strong>in epic battles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>CUSTOMIZE YOUR LOOK</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303010/extras/scroll05.png?t=1735350370\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Change your appearance</strong> with different outfits: kimonos, armors, hats, masks, dresses and much more.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>EQUIP &amp; UPGRADE YOUR DRAGON GEMS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303010/extras/scroll06.png?t=1735350370\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Boost your stats</strong> using the power contained in<strong> Dragon Gems</strong>. Get them in different forms, sets, and rarities to suit your combat style.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>BEWARE WITH CURSED SEALS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303010/extras/scroll07.png?t=1735350370\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Cursed Seals</strong> are powerful but dangerous items which you can benefit from their power as you deal with his <strong>curse</strong>. No pain, no gain!</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303010/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1735350370","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3303010/page.bg.jpg?t=1735350370","capsule_image":"htt